pageTitle: Intel® Desktop Board D865GBF — System Memory
textBeforeTable: DDR400, DDR333, and DDR266 SDRAM DIMMs. Serial presence detect. Non-ECC DIMMs. Minimum total system memory: 64 MB. 4 GB maximum total system memory. Unbuffered, single-sided or double-sided DIMMs with the following restriction: Double-sided DIMMs with x16 organization are not supported. 2.6V (only) 184-pin DDR SDRAM DIMMs with gold-plated contacts.
